531
00:34:01,720 --> 00:34:04,080
Right... In a bag.

532
00:34:04,680 --> 00:34:07,160
He gave me a prune. Howard Hughes.

533
00:34:07,240 --> 00:34:10,920
Dick is jumping forward a little bit.
It was a memorable moment for him.

534
00:34:11,040 --> 00:34:14,680
