538
00:34:21,920 --> 00:34:23,040
He gave me a prune.

539
00:34:23,160 --> 00:34:25,960
Howard Hughes gave me a prune
on the beach at Nassau.

540
00:34:26,560 --> 00:34:29,760
I thought you met Hughes
the first time in Mexico.

541
00:34:33,840 --> 00:34:36,520
Ralph, what happened was this.
I got a phone call.

542
00:34:36,640 --> 00:34:38,160
Really, out of the blue.

543
00:34:38,240 --> 00:34:41,560
From a man
named George Gordon Holmes.

544
00:34:41,720 --> 00:34:43,760
Longtime associate of Howard Hughes.

545
00:34:44,000 --> 00:34:46,560
He says he wants us
to fly down to Mexico City,

546
00:34:47,160 --> 00:34:49,880
